foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The Department became aware during FY 14 that a few bureaus had failed to enter FOIA requests into the Department's Electronic FOIA Tracking System in a timely fashion. The Department has therefore determined that the total number of requests in FY 14 was greater than initially identified. The Department is working expeditiously to address its expanded workload. (Some other bureaus made entries that resulted in minor adjustments to the number of requests they had received and were pending at the start of FY 14, but these adjustments only slightly affect this expanded workload.)
